      • sap_ui_commons_Tree_getNodes_Rec

        public static java.lang.String sap_ui_commons_Tree_getNodes_Rec(boolean includeDependency)
        Generate a tree hierarchy structure from a sap tree object. A sap tree object is already
        a tree-hierarchy structure, but it contains too many information, and it is super-time-consuming
        when return it to Java side by Selenium. So we will create a light-tree-structure to contain
        only the necessary information thru this function.

        depending on:
        #parse_sap_ui_commons_TreeNode(boolean)

        depending level: 1
        Parameters:
        nodeObject - (Javascript) Object, SAP Tree/TreeNode Object.
        node - (Javascript) Object, has structure of org.safs.selenium.webdriver.lib.model.TreeNode and represents the first parameter nodeObject, it will contain all children of nodeObject.
